nayak ( assamese : &lt;unk&gt; , english : the eastern sun ) is a 1959 assamese film directed by prabhat mukherjee of &lt;unk&gt; and released in 1959 . the film was directed by prabhat mukherjee of &lt;unk&gt; and released in 1959 . it was the first assamese film to win the national film award for best feature film in assamese .